features: The Zinc Air batteries deliver a consistently high level of power and are supremely suitable for the latest generation of Bluetooth hearing aids
These batteries are ideally suited to operate mini BTE (behind the ear)
The Zinc Air battery delivers reliable power in different temperature conditions, so that users can enjoy outdoor activities for longer
To use: pull off the tab and wait approximately 60 seconds. This activates the battery by allowing oxygen to enter.
Panasonic is constantly developing innovative ideas for reducing the amount of harmful materials, and this is why there is 0% mercury in the Zinc Air battery.
